# Welcome to the CEFR Level Classifier Project! ðŸš€
This project, built with Streamlit, uses a three-phase Camembert AI model to classify French texts according to the six CEFR levels (A1, A2, B1, B2, C1, and C2).
# CEFR Explanation
CEFR (Common European Framework of Reference for Languages) is a global standard for language ability assessment.
